p.s.---Scientists are rarely right about anything.  Instead of experimenting and trying things themselves, they feel they are superior to the researchers and can judge every move we make without doing anything.  I don&#39;t mind the blind testing, it&#39;s that something speaks and makes sense that shouldn&#39;t is my fascination with this.  If you had a 68&#39; mustang parked on your monitor and they said it was an ice cream cone, it still was a voice that responded to my question....whether right or wrong.

-Steve H.




